# -------------------------------------------------
# Platform Routing (used for platform-scoped APIs)
# -------------------------------------------------
# Examples:
#   euw1  â†’ Europe West
#   eun1  â†’ Europe Nordic & East
#   na1   â†’ North America
#   kr    â†’ Korea
#   jp1   â†’ Japan
