# -------------------------------------------------
# Regional Routing (used for region-scoped APIs)
# -------------------------------------------------
# Examples:
#   europe   â†’ EUW/EUNE/TR/RU
#   americas â†’ NA/BR/LA/OC
#   asia     â†’ KR/JP
# -------------------------------------------------
# Leave empty to auto-map based on platform
